Before you can connect Alexa with POWERbot-S, please kindly follow below steps:
a. Download "POWERbot-S" app from Google Play or App Store;
b. Sign up or sign in with your "POWERbot-S" App account;
c. Setup the device with your "POWERbot-S" app, and make sure you can control it by the app;
d. Open Alexa app, search "POWERbot-S" skill and enable it by signing in with the same ID you used in "POWERbot-S" app.
e. When setup is ready, try ask Alexa to control your devices.
